# Connecting via Wired LAN (Ethernet)

Connect to Frame.io via wired LAN (Ethernet).

1. Connect to the network by plugging an Ethernet cable into the camera’s LAN connector.

2. Select **Frame.io Camera to Cloud > CONNECT**.

   !Frame.io Camera to Cloud Menu

3. Select **WIRED LAN**.

   !Wired LAN Selection

4. Adjust **IP ADDRESS SETTING**.
   - Select **AUTO** to use an IP address assigned by the network.
   - Select **MANUAL** to choose the IP address manually as described in “Connecting Using an IP Address” (page 273).

   !IP Address Setting

5. Once connected, select **GET PAIRING CODE**.

   !Get Pairing Code

   A pairing code will be displayed.
